snippet.title: Sword Of Symphony - Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
All links: https://linktr.ee/swordofsymphony

Introducing a new music-action RPG called Sword Of Symphony!

So far, all that I’m revealing about the game is that explores the concept of using character-action gameplay to compose music.

It's also deeply connected to the story of Purpose: VERSUS (another one of my IPs), though *how* is currently a secret...
